goals.title: Lose weight
goals.description: You'd like to lose at least 10 to 15 pounds (or more).

goals.title: Build muscle
goals.description: You'd like to build muscle and increase your overall body weight.

goals.title: Athletic Performance
goals.description: You want optimal nutrition to support long and intense athletic training. (Minimal to no weight change desired.)

goals.title: Body Recomposition
goals.description: You want to lose less than 10 to 15 pounds of body fat, while simultaneously building muscle.

goals.title: Improve Health
goals.description: You want to improve your nutrition and overall health, while maintaining your current weight.

activitylevels.title: Light
activitylevels.description: 1-3 hours of gentle to moderaate exercise

activitylevels.title: Intense
activitylevels.description: 4-6 hours of moderate to strenuous exercise
